ciscoAal5MIB.name: ciscoAal5MIB

revisions.description: Added following objects in cAal5VccTable: cAal5VccHCInPkts, cAal5VccHCOutPkts, cAal5VccHCInOctets, cAal5VccHCOutOctets
Latest version of this MIB module with extended support for vc drop stats.
Initial version of this MIB module.

ciscoAal5MIB.contactinfo: Cisco Systems Customer Service Postal: 170 W Tasman Drive San Jose, CA 95134 USA Tel: +1 800 553-NETS E-mail: cs-atm@cisco.com
ciscoAal5MIB.description: Cisco Enterprise AAL5 MIB file that provide AAL5 specific information that are either excluded by RFC 1695 or specific to Cisco product.

cAal5VccTable.name: cAal5VccTable
cAal5VccTable.description: This table contains AAL5 VCC performance parameters beyond that provided by aal5VccEntry defined in RFC1695.

cAal5VccEntry.name: cAal5VccEntry
cAal5VccEntry.description: This list contains the additional AAL5 VCC performance parameters beyond that provided by aal5VccEntry defined in RFC1695.

cAal5VccInPkts.name: cAal5VccInPkts
cAal5VccInPkts.description: The number of AAL5 CPCS PDUs received on this AAL5 VCC at the interface associated with an AAL5 entity.

cAal5VccOutPkts.name: cAal5VccOutPkts
cAal5VccOutPkts.description: The number of AAL5 CPCS PDUs transmitted on this AAL5 VCC at the interface associated with an AAL5 entity.

cAal5VccInOctets.name: cAal5VccInOctets
cAal5VccInOctets.description: The number of AAL5 CPCS PDU octets received on this AAL5 VCC at the interface associated with an AAL5 entity.

cAal5VccOutOctets.name: cAal5VccOutOctets
cAal5VccOutOctets.description: The number of AAL5 CPCS PDU octets transmitted on this AAL5 VCC at the interface associated with an AAL5 entity.

cAal5VccInDroppedPkts.name: cAal5VccInDroppedPkts
cAal5VccInDroppedPkts.description: The number of AAL5 CPCS PDUs dropped at the receive side of this AAL5 VCC at the interface associated with an AAL5 entity.

cAal5VccOutDroppedPkts.name: cAal5VccOutDroppedPkts
cAal5VccOutDroppedPkts.description: The number of AAL5 CPCS PDUs dropped at the transmit side of this AAL5 VCC at the interface associated with an AAL5 entity.

cAal5VccInDroppedOctets.name: cAal5VccInDroppedOctets
cAal5VccInDroppedOctets.description: The number of AAL5 CPCS PDU Octets dropped at the receive side of this AAL5 VCC at the interface associated with an AAL5 entity.

cAal5VccOutDroppedOctets.name: cAal5VccOutDroppedOctets
cAal5VccOutDroppedOctets.description: The number of AAL5 CPCS PDU Octets dropped at the transmit side of this AAL5 VCC at the interface associated with an AAL5 entity.

cAal5VccHCInPkts.name: cAal5VccHCInPkts
cAal5VccHCInPkts.description: This is 64bit (High Capacity) version of cAal5VccInPkts counters.

cAal5VccHCOutPkts.name: cAal5VccHCOutPkts
cAal5VccHCOutPkts.description: This is 64bit (High Capacity) version of cAal5VccOutPkts counters.

cAal5VccHCInOctets.name: cAal5VccHCInOctets
cAal5VccHCInOctets.description: This is 64bit (High Capacity) version of cAal5VccInOctets counters.

cAal5VccHCOutOctets.name: cAal5VccHCOutOctets
cAal5VccHCOutOctets.description: This is 64bit (High Capacity) version of cAal5VccOutOctets counters.

ciscoAal5MIBCompliance.name: ciscoAal5MIBCompliance
ciscoAal5MIBCompliance.description: The compliance statement for entities which implement this Cisco AAL5 MIB.

ciscoAal5MIBComplianceRev1.name: ciscoAal5MIBComplianceRev1
ciscoAal5MIBComplianceRev1.description: The compliance statement for entities which implement this Cisco AAL5 MIB.

ciscoAal5MIBComplianceRev2.name: ciscoAal5MIBComplianceRev2
ciscoAal5MIBComplianceRev2.description: The compliance statement for entities which implement 64bit counters for Vcc received/transmit PDU and octets objects for Cisco AAL5 MIB.

ciscoAal5MIBGroup.name: ciscoAal5MIBGroup
ciscoAal5MIBGroup.description: A collection of objects providing AAL5 related parameters.

ciscoAal5VcStatsExtMIBGroup.name: ciscoAal5VcStatsExtMIBGroup
ciscoAal5VcStatsExtMIBGroup.description: A collection of objects providing extension to AAL5 related vc drop statistics

ciscoAal5MIBHCGroup.name: ciscoAal5MIBHCGroup
ciscoAal5MIBHCGroup.description: A collection of objects providing 64bit AAL5 related parameters.
